CatDescriptText: First row left to right: Johnny Goode, Robert Lavelle, Anna Lavella, Rosalia "Cookie" Goode, Allan Goode, Sharon Goode (Ryan), Roberta Goode; second row in center, Wilhelmina "Billie" Goode, , Russell Goode wearing eyeglasses; back row second from left: Sara Jane McPherson Goode, Mary Goode, Mal Goode wearing eyeglasses, Jim Goode, Ruth Goode White, Julia wearing dark short sleeved dress, and William W. TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Goode family, with women, children, and men, in honor of Mal Goode and Mary Lavelle Goode's anniversary in their home
